reviewText:
1st step: buy The Binding Of Isaac: Rebirth;
2nd step: go on YouTube and search for Northernlion;
3rd step: watch Northernlion's videos;
4th step: play The Binding Of Isaac Rebirth until your keyboard breaks;
5th step: realise you have watched Northernlion playing isaac more time than your total hours in the game.

11/10 would kill spiders again.
